{"tid":1226033,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個/幾個覺得好撚柒嘅簡體字","createTime":"2019-06-15T09:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T23:29:39.000Z","uid":251510,"like":125,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"4341cef39cb1d0c0ac0ce097a800ad915908205e","tid":1226033,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:25:45.000Z","msg":"我先：稳（穩定嘅「穩」）<br />\n想國家穩定，政府推行嘅政策就唔可以操之過急。想行路行得穩，唔好咁易跌平衡仆親，亦唔應該行得太急。人做事，想辦得穩妥，亦應該三思而後行，一味心急就容易釀成大錯。<br />\n<br />\n但偏偏，簡體字嘅「穩（稳）」入面就包含咗個「急」字。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2afa67fc85b25250ad1e9164ec6aca4b68cc58","tid":1226033,"uid":150100,"like":120,"dislike":3,"score":117,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:30:21.000Z","msg":"All<br />\n除咗点<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37e25d6f564bd72113b96f6b9b0b07a7eb323d7","tid":1226033,"uid":196924,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:31:20.000Z","msg":"愛無心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695fdfb5eaa9583740e52ef1c191c00eee855c89","tid":1226033,"uid":251510,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:32:33.000Z","msg":"其實應該轉一轉個標題：一人一個/幾個覺得特別柒嘅簡體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd054e92cca2fc556232425cd929b7155477cbc","tid":1226033,"uid":124690,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:35:48.000Z","msg":"国"},{"pid":"872d6d9e005ad5ae9df5428e28ef141402db2fdf","tid":1226033,"uid":220236,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:41:20.000Z","msg":"够 唔知有乜意義"},{"pid":"44080990eb747ece8b917a240f0ecceb480ece65","tid":1226033,"uid":251510,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"872d6d9e005ad5ae9df5428e28ef141402db2fdf","tid":1226033,"uid":220236,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:41:20.000Z","msg":"够 唔知有乜意義"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"